# Osman Hadi Archive | ‡¶ì‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶¶‡¶ø ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶≠

<p align="center">
  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mahadi99900/Osman_Hadi/main/pic.jpg" width="300" alt="Shaheed Osman Bin Hadi">
</p>


**Osman Hadi Archive** is a Python library that documents and showcases the life, achievements, and revolutionary activities of Osman Hadi. It uses ASCII art, banners, and structured textual content to make console output engaging. The library is fully bilingual (English & Bengali) and designed for educational and commemorative purposes. **‡¶ì‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶¶‡¶ø ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶≠** ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶•‡¶® ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞‡¶ø ‡¶Ø‡¶æ ‡¶ì‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡ßÄ‡¶¨‡¶®, ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶Æ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶£‡ßç‡¶° ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßç‡¶≤‡¶¨‡ßÄ ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶Æ ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶¶‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶∂‡¶® ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§ ‡¶è‡¶§‡ßá ASCII ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ü, ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶∏‡¶Ç‡¶∞‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∑‡¶ø‡¶§ ‡¶§‡¶•‡ßç‡¶Ø ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶≤ ‡¶Ü‡¶â‡¶ü‡¶™‡ßÅ‡¶ü‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶Ü‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶∑‡¶£‡ßÄ‡¶Ø‡¶º ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ ‡¶π‡¶Ø‡¶º‡ßá‡¶õ‡ßá‡•§ ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶¶‡ßÅ‡¶á ‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶∑‡¶æ‡¶Ø‡¶º (‡¶á‡¶Ç‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶ú‡¶ø ‡¶ì ‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶≤‡¶æ) ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶Ø‡ßã‡¶ó‡ßç‡¶Ø‡•§  

## Modules & Functions | ‡¶Æ‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶â‡¶≤ ‡¶ì ‡¶´‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶∂‡¶®‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßÇ‡¶π

- **`osman_hadi.family("b")`** : Displays Osman Hadi's family background and personal life. Set `lang='e'` for English. / ‡¶ì‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶ú‡ßÄ‡¶¨‡¶® ‡¶ì ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶ó‡¶§ ‡¶§‡¶•‡ßç‡¶Ø ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§ `lang='e'` ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶á‡¶Ç‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶ú‡¶ø‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶Ü‡¶â‡¶ü‡¶™‡ßÅ‡¶ü‡•§  
- **`osman_edu(lang='b')`** : Shows educational journey, academic achievements, and scholarly milestones. / ‡¶∂‡¶ø‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∑‡¶æ‡¶ú‡ßÄ‡¶¨‡¶®, ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶°‡ßá‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶Ö‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ú‡¶® ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶Ü‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Æ‡¶ø milestones ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶¶‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶∂‡¶® ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§  
- **`osman_hadi.initiatives(lang='b')`** : Highlights strategic initiatives, social campaigns, and movements led by Osman Hadi. / ‡¶ì‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶®‡ßá‡¶§‡ßÉ‡¶§‡ßç‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶®‡ßá‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ ‡¶ï‡ßå‡¶∂‡¶≤‡¶ó‡¶§ ‡¶â‡¶¶‡ßç‡¶Ø‡ßã‡¶ó, ‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶ú‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶ì ‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßà‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶Ü‡¶®‡ßç‡¶¶‡ßã‡¶≤‡¶® ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§  
- **`osman_hadi.july_hadi(lang='b')`** : Presents Osman Hadi's role in the 2024 July Uprising and documents the crimes of the regime. / ‡ß®‡ß¶‡ß®‡ß™ ‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶á ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßç‡¶≤‡¶¨ ‡¶ì ‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶≠‡ßÇ‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶ï‡¶æ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶∏‡¶∞‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ö‡¶™‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ß ‡¶®‡¶•‡¶ø‡¶≠‡ßÅ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§  
- **`osman_hadi.quotes(lang='b')`** : Shows iconic quotes, legendary sayings, and humanitarian activities of Osman Hadi. / ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶ú‡¶Ø‡¶º‡ßÄ ‡¶â‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§‡¶ø, ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶¶ ‡¶ì ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶Æ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶£‡ßç‡¶° ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§  

## Installation & Import | ‡¶á‡¶®‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶∂‡¶® ‡¶ì ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡¶™‡ßã‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ü

Install directly via pip / ‡¶∏‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶∏‡¶∞‡¶ø pip ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶Ø‡¶º‡ßá ‡¶á‡¶®‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßÅ‡¶®:  
`pip install osman_hadi`  

Import the modules in your Python script / ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶•‡¶® ‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá ‡¶Æ‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶â‡¶≤‡¶ó‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡¶™‡ßã‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßÅ‡¶®:  
`from osman_hadi import osman_family, osman_edu, osman_initiatives, osman_july, osman_quotes`  
`from osman_hadi.styles import his_face1, his_face2, his_face3, his_face4, his_face5`  

## Usage | ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶∞

**Display Family Information / ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶§‡¶•‡ßç‡¶Ø **  
`osman_hadi.family(lang='b')  # Bengali`  
`osman_hadi.family(lang='e')  # English`  

**Display Educational Background / ‡¶∂‡¶ø‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∑‡¶æ‡¶ú‡ßÄ‡¶¨‡¶® **  
`osman_edu.edu(lang='b')  # Bengali`  
`osman_edu.edu(lang='e')  # English`  

**Display Strategic Initiatives / ‡¶ï‡ßå‡¶∂‡¶≤‡¶ó‡¶§ ‡¶â‡¶¶‡ßç‡¶Ø‡ßã‡¶ó **  
`osman_hadi.initiatives(lang='b')  # Bengali`  
`osman_hadi.initiatives(lang='e')  # English`  

**Show July Uprising & Historical Events / ‡¶ú‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶á ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßç‡¶≤‡¶¨ ‡¶ì ‡¶ê‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶∏‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶ò‡¶ü‡¶®‡¶æ **  
`osman_hadi.july_hadi(lang='b')  # Bengali`  
`osman_hadi.july_hadi(lang='e')  # English`  

**Show Quotes & Humanitarian Activities / ‡¶â‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§‡¶ø ‡¶ì ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶Æ **  
`osman_hadi.quotes(lang='b')  # Bengali`  
`osman_hadi.quotes(lang='e')  # English`  

## Banner & Faces | ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ì ‡¶Æ‡ßÅ‡¶ñ‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ü

Each module automatically prints an ASCII banner and one of Osman Hadi's faces when called. The `styles.py` file includes: `his_face1(), his_face2(), his_face3(), his_face4(), his_face5(), `. These are used internally by each module for visual effects, but can also be called independently for custom display. / ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶Æ‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶â‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶¨‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ASCII ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶ì‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶Æ‡ßÅ‡¶ñ ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§ `styles.py` ‡¶´‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶∞‡¶Ø‡¶º‡ßá‡¶õ‡ßá: `his_face1(), his_face2(), his_face3(), his_face4(), his_face5(), `. ‡¶è‡¶ó‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶Æ‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶â‡¶≤‡¶ó‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡ßã‡¶∞ ‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶ú‡ßç‡¶Ø‡ßÅ‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶≤ ‡¶á‡¶´‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶π‡ßÉ‡¶§ ‡¶π‡¶Ø‡¶º, ‡¶ï‡¶ø‡¶®‡ßç‡¶§‡ßÅ ‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶¨‡¶§‡¶®‡ßç‡¶§‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶Æ ‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶™‡ßç‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶ì ‡¶ï‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ ‡¶Ø‡ßá‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§  

